Agent Roles
AgentProviderResponsibilityPredictive Agent (orchestrator)Groq — llama3-8b-8192Talks to user, coordinates the other two, reasons about vehicle future stateSafety AgentOllama — phi3:miniMonitors live sensors, fires emergency alerts, watches thresholdsPreventive AgentOllama — phi3:miniTracks maintenance schedules, part wear, upcoming service needs


How They Communicate
User
 │
 ▼
Predictive Agent (Groq)
 ├── consult_safety_agent()   ──► Safety Agent (Ollama)
 │                                 tools: live sensors, thresholds, event log
 └── consult_preventive_agent() ► Preventive Agent (Ollama)
                                   tools: maintenance schedule, part history, mileage


File Structure
acdt_camry/
├── .env
├── main.py                          # starts everything
├── config/
│   └── ditto/
│       ├── nginx.conf
│       └── nginx.htpasswd
├── shared/
│   ├── config.py                    # sensor fields, thresholds, constants
│   ├── influx_io.py                 # InfluxDB read/write
│   ├── mongo_io.py                  # MongoDB events
│   └── redis_io.py                  # Redis cache
├── physical/
│   └── simulator.py                 # OBD-II simulator → direct InfluxDB
├── intelligent/
│   ├── neo4j_kg.py                  # knowledge graph
│   ├── safety_agent.py              # Safety Agent (Ollama)
│   ├── preventive_agent.py          # Preventive Agent (Ollama)
│   └── predictive_agent.py          # Predictive Agent (Groq) — orchestrator
├── service_layer/
│   ├── ditto_client.py
│   ├── ditto_sync.py
│   └── agent_api.py                 # FastAPI + SSE streaming
└── ui/
    └── dashboard.html               # Full HUD dashboard + live charts + chat



